---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<!-- Hero / Overture: pain-led headline with portrait, anchors the whole case for hiring -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-12 md:pt-20 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <!-- Issue heading -->
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-10 md:mb-16" data-reveal>
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <span class="small-caps text-ink-muted">Vol. I</span>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-ink-muted font-mono text-[11px]">&middot;</span>
        <span class="hidden md:inline small-caps text-ink-muted">Executive support, reimagined</span>
      </div>
      <span class="small-caps text-ink-muted tabular">2026</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-end">
      <!-- Left: pain-led display headline -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7" data-reveal>
        <p class="small-caps text-copper mb-6">The Dossier</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-[12vw] md:text-[6.5rem] lg:text-[8rem] text-ink leading-[0.92] tracking-[-0.035em]">
          The executive office
          <br/>should run on
          <span class="italic font-display-italic text-copper">systems</span>,
          <br/>not heroics.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-10 md:mt-12 text-lg md:text-xl text-ink-soft leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          If board prep is a quarterly fire drill, if earnings coordination lives in someone's head, if your EA function was built for the company you were two funding rounds ago, we should talk.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          I rebuild the three things that break first as executive offices scale: <span class="text-ink font-medium">board cadence</span>, <span class="text-ink font-medium">investor-relations coordination</span>, and the <span class="text-ink font-medium">EA function itself</span>. Twelve years of doing this for pre-IPO biotech, public-company cannabis, and Big Four.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 md:mt-14 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="#two-paths"
            class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-ink text-paper px-7 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-copper transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Part-time or full-time hire</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href={`${base}services`}
            class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-paper border-2 border-ink text-ink px-7 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper transition-colors"
          >
            <span>See fractional services</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: portrait + caption block -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5" data-reveal>
        <figure class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-[2px] overflow-hidden bg-paper-deep shadow-[0_20px_60px_-20px_rgba(22,21,19,0.25)]">
            <img
              src={`${base}portrait.jpg`}
              alt="Leigh-Ann Martin"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              style="object-position: center top;"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Caption with editorial rule -->
          <figcaption class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-ink/20">
            <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink-muted mb-1">Portrait</p>
            <p class="font-caption text-sm text-ink-soft italic leading-snug">
              Leigh-Ann Martin, New York, 2026. Senior Executive Assistant. Fractional partner. Founding Member and Lead of Immunovant's Culture Committee.
            </p>
          </figcaption>

          <!-- Floating badge -->
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 top-6 bg-copper text-paper px-3 py-1.5 rotate-[-4deg] shadow-lg">
            <span class="small-caps text-paper">Available now</span>
          </div>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Lower strip: the three things she fixes -->
    <div class="mt-16 md:mt-24 pt-8 border-t border-rule" data-reveal>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-copper mb-3">She fixes 01</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl text-ink leading-tight">Board cadence that doesn't exist yet.</p>
          <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Quarterly rhythm, 12-month forward calendar, audit and compensation committees wired.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-copper mb-3">She fixes 02</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl text-ink leading-tight">Earnings comms that live in someone's head.</p>
          <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">6 to 8 week repeatable prep cadence, external IR alignment, stakeholder access.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-copper mb-3">She fixes 03</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl text-ink leading-tight">An EA function built for yesterday.</p>
          <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">First-hire or scale-up. Onboarding framework, knowledge base, team cadence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
